channel.description:
Inspired by the fantastic work of TG Tales and so many other talented TG artists out there, I began re-purposing movies and video footage by creating re-imagined edits of them using TG themes on my own site...

http://www.TGCreation.com/
(If visiting my site, please be aware that it contains sexually explicit material.)

My YouTube channel contains exclusive new videos that aren't on my other site and is meant for a broader audience.  Please keep an open mind and a sense of humor as you view them.  The videos I create are entirely fictional.

The videos posted here are edits, mash-ups and parodies meant strictly for entertainment purposes. The use of the original source material is intended to fall under the guidelines of "fair use" or "fair dealing" of various international Copyright Acts. If you are the actual copyright holder of any of the material I've used and would like it removed, please contact me and I'll respect your wishes.

Truly,
Wren
